### 🎯 Application (Use Cases & Business Logic)

**Purpose:** Orchestrate domain operations, enforce business rules, fire domain events.

**Folder Structure:**

```
Application/
├─ Services/             # Application services (use cases)
│  ├─ TodoService.cs
│  └─ IEventBusAdapter.cs
├─ Interfaces/           # Abstraction contracts
│  ├─ ITodoService.cs
│  └─ IEventBus.cs
└─ DTOs/                 # Data transfer objects
   └─ TodoDto.cs
```

**Service Example:**

```csharp
// Application/Services/TodoService.cs
public class TodoService : ITodoService
{
    private readonly ITodoRepository _repository;
    private readonly IEventBus _eventBus;
    
    public TodoService(ITodoRepository repository, IEventBus eventBus)
    {
        _repository = repository;
        _eventBus = eventBus;
    }
    
    public async Task<IEnumerable<TodoItem>> GetAllTodosAsync()
    {
        return await _repository.GetAllAsync();
    }
    
    public async Task CreateTodoAsync(string title)
    {
        // Business rule: title required
        if (string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(title))
            throw new ArgumentException("Title is required", nameof(title));
        
        var todo = new TodoItem
        {
            Title = title,
            CreatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow,
            IsComplete = false
        };
        
        await _repository.AddAsync(todo);
        await _repository.SaveChangesAsync();
        
        // Fire domain event
        _eventBus.Fire(DomainEvents.TodoCreated);
    }
    
    public async Task ToggleTodoAsync(int id)
    {
        var todo = await _repository.GetByIdAsync(id);
        if (todo == null)
            throw new KeyNotFoundException($"Todo {id} not found");
        
        todo.IsComplete = !todo.IsComplete;
        await _repository.SaveChangesAsync();
        
        _eventBus.Fire(DomainEvents.TodoUpdated);
    }
}
```

**Key Responsibilities:**
- Implement use cases (CreateTodo, ToggleTodo, etc.)
- Enforce business rules
- Orchestrate domain operations
- Fire domain events via `IEventBus`
- Coordinate repository calls
- NO direct DbContext access
- NO HTTP/view concerns

