### 🔧 Infrastructure (Data Access)

**Purpose:** Implement data access, database context, repository implementations.

**Folder Structure:**

```
Infrastructure/
├─ Data/                 # EF Core context
│  ├─ AppDbContext.cs
│  └─ Seeders/
│     └─ SeedRunner.cs
├─ Repositories/         # Repository implementations
│  └─ TodoRepository.cs
└─ Migrations/           # EF Core migrations
   └─ 20250106_InitialCreate.cs
```

**DbContext Example:**

```csharp
// Infrastructure/Data/AppDbContext.cs
public class AppDbContext : DbContext
{
    public AppDbContext(DbContextOptions<AppDbContext> options)
        : base(options)
    {
    }
    
    public DbSet<TodoItem> TodoItems => Set<TodoItem>();
    
    protected override void OnModelCreating(ModelBuilder modelBuilder)
    {
        base.OnModelCreating(modelBuilder);
        
        modelBuilder.Entity<TodoItem>(entity =>
        {
            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);
            entity.Property(e => e.Title).IsRequired().HasMaxLength(500);
            entity.HasIndex(e => e.IsComplete);
        });
    }
}
```

**Repository Implementation:**

```csharp
// Infrastructure/Repositories/TodoRepository.cs
public class TodoRepository : ITodoRepository
{
    private readonly AppDbContext _context;
    
    public TodoRepository(AppDbContext context)
    {
        _context = context;
    }
    
    public async Task<IEnumerable<TodoItem>> GetAllAsync()
    {
        return await _context.TodoItems
            .OrderByDescending(t => t.CreatedAt)
            .ToListAsync();
    }
    
    public async Task<TodoItem?> GetByIdAsync(int id)
    {
        return await _context.TodoItems.FindAsync(id);
    }
    
    public async Task AddAsync(TodoItem todo)
    {
        await _context.TodoItems.AddAsync(todo);
    }
    
    public async Task UpdateAsync(TodoItem todo)
    {
        _context.TodoItems.Update(todo);
    }
    
    public async Task DeleteAsync(int id)
    {
        var todo = await GetByIdAsync(id);
        if (todo != null)
            _context.TodoItems.Remove(todo);
    }
    
    public async Task SaveChangesAsync()
    {
        await _context.SaveChangesAsync();
    }
}
```

**Key Responsibilities:**
- Implement `DbContext` (EF Core)
- Implement repository interfaces from Domain
- Handle database migrations
- Data seeding
- NO business logic
- NO HTTP/view concerns

